issues.description: The constructor in the solution repository has parameters in a different order than specified in the UML diagram of the problem statement, which could confuse students about the required order for implementing the constructor as per the exercise instructions.
issues.suggested_fix: Modify the constructor in the solution repository to match the parameter order from the UML diagram: String lectureName, int numberOfInscribedStudents, int numberOfGuestStudents, int numberOfLecturers, int numberOfTutors.
